Name: Average resolution time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with 'Completed + Closed' as final activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Minimum duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Maximum duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases that also include 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to reach 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in 'Unmatched + Unmatched' across all variants leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Longest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Completed' activity
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed'

Name: Shortest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases that transition through 'Accepted + Assigned' before completing
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with high impact as described in the event log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the variant with the highest performance leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled' versus those ending with 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Cancelled occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases from France compared to cases from Brazil
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the shortest and longest process variants as described
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Cycle time of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in processes leading to 'Completed + In Call' with medium impact as described in the event log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
